race.description: Road To Magic Millions Book Now Handicap (Bm68)
race.comment: Plenty of win chances. JUST PRECIOUS (1) is well placed here on recent form. Won similar grade three back then last two in richer company, the latest when wide throughout here in a hot form race behind Lucifer which has already seen five subsequent winners. Has the claim and the figures to go close. BLUE ALLURE (6) found the 1000m a bit sharp fresh when spotted a start but motored home in an eye-catching second. Placed 2/3 second-up and expected to be winding up hard again. THE ENCHANTER (2) had first run here last time and while fifth was close to the winner. This easier and has the inside gate this time for the hot apprentice. Take catching. WISNIERSKA (9) was a close-up third here two back then seventh in richer company on the Gold Coast last time. Very attractively weighted.
